#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.91"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.91:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.91:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.91:0.3"
msgid "91. Saṅkavāsutta"
msgstr "91. At Paṅkadhā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.237"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: saṅkavā → paṅkadhā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.91:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṃghena "
"saddhiṃ yena saṅkavā nāma kosalānaṃ nigamo tadavasari."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Kosalans together "
"with a large Saṅgha of mendicants. He arrived at a town of the Kosalans "
"named Paṅkadhā,"

msgctxt "an3.91:1.2"
msgid "Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā saṅkavāyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "and stayed there."

msgctxt "an3.91:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena kassapagotto nāma bhikkhu saṅkavāyaṃ āvāsiko hoti."
msgstr "Now, at that time a monk called Kassapagotta was resident at Paṅkadhā."

msgctxt "an3.91:1.4"
msgid ""
"Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū "
"sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti."
msgstr ""
"There the Buddha educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired the mendicants "
"with a Dhamma talk about the training rules."

msgctxt "an3.91:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kassapagottassa bhikkhuno bhagavati sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya "
"dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū sandassente samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente "
"ahudeva akkhanti ahu appaccayo:"
msgstr "Kassapagotta became quite impatient and bitter, thinking:"

#. VAR: adhisallikhatevāyaṃ → adhisallekhatevāyaṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "an3.91:1.6"
msgid "“adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo”ti."
msgstr "“This ascetic is much too strict.”"

msgctxt "an3.91:1.7"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā saṅkavāyaṃ yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā yena rājagahaṃ tena "
"cārikaṃ pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"When the Buddha had stayed in Paṅkadhā as long as he wished, he set out for "
"Rājagaha."

msgctxt "an3.91:1.8"
msgid "Anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena rājagahaṃ tadavasari."
msgstr "Travelling stage by stage, he arrived at Rājagaha,"

msgctxt "an3.91:1.9"
msgid "Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati."
msgstr "and stayed there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kassapagottassa bhikkhuno acirapakkantassa bhagavato ahudeva "
"kukkuccaṃ ahu vippaṭisāro:"
msgstr ""
"Soon after the Buddha left, Kassapagotta became quite remorseful and "
"regretful, thinking:"

msgctxt "an3.91:2.2"
msgid ""
"“alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
msgstr "“It’s my loss, my misfortune, "

msgctxt "an3.91:2.3"
msgid ""
"yassa me bhagavati sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū "
"sandassente samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente ahudeva akkhanti ahu "
"appaccayo:"
msgstr ""
"that when the Buddha was talking about the training rules I became quite "
"impatient and bitter, thinking"

msgctxt "an3.91:2.4"
msgid "‘adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo’ti."
msgstr "he was much too strict."

msgctxt "an3.91:2.5"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike "
"accayaṃ accayato deseyyan”ti."
msgstr "Why don’t I go to the Buddha and confess my mistake to him?”"

msgctxt "an3.91:2.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho kassapagotto bhikkhu senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"rājagahaṃ tena pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then Kassapagotta set his lodgings in order and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"set out for Rājagaha."

msgctxt "an3.91:2.7"
msgid ""
"Anupubbena yena rājagahaṃ yena gijjhakūṭo pabbato yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
" upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno "
"kho kassapagotto bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Eventually he came to Rājagaha and the Vulture’s Peak. He went up to the "
"Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.238"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Ekamidaṃ, bhante, samayaṃ bhagavā saṅkavāyaṃ viharati, saṅkavā nāma "
"kosalānaṃ nigamo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tatra, bhante, bhagavā sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū "
"sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ bhagavati sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū "
"sandassente samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente ahudeva akkhanti ahu "
"appaccayo:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.4"
msgid "‘adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo’ti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: () → (anupubbena cārikaṃ caramāno yena rājagahaṃ tadavasari. tatra sudaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati. atha kho) (mr)
msgctxt "an3.91:3.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā saṅkavāyaṃ yathābhirantaṃ viharitvā yena rājagahaṃ tena "
"cārikaṃ pakkāmi. ()"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.6"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, acirapakkantassa bhagavato ahudeva kukkuccaṃ ahu "
"vippaṭisāro:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.7"
msgid ""
"‘alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.8"
msgid ""
"yassa me bhagavati sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū "
"sandassente samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente ahudeva akkhanti ahu "
"appaccayo:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.9"
msgid "“adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.10"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike "
"accayaṃ accayato deseyyan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:3.11"
msgid ""
"Accayo maṃ, bhante, accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ yassa me "
"bhagavati sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū sandassente "
"samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente ahudeva akkhanti ahu appaccayo:"
msgstr ""
"I have made a mistake, sir. It was foolish, stupid, and unskillful of me to "
"become impatient and bitter when the Buddha was educating, encouraging, "
"firing up, and inspiring the mendicants with a Dhamma talk about the "
"training rules, and to think:"

msgctxt "an3.91:3.12"
msgid "‘adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo’ti."
msgstr "‘This ascetic is much too strict.’"

msgctxt "an3.91:3.13"
msgid ""
"Tassa me, bhante, bhagavā accayaṃ accayato paṭiggaṇhātu, āyatiṃ saṃvarāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Please, sir, accept my mistake for what it is, so I will restrain myself in "
"future.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Taggha taṃ → taggha tvaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.91:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha taṃ, kassapa, accayo accagamā yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, "
"yassa te mayi sikkhāpadapaṭisaṃyuttāya dhammiyā kathāya bhikkhū sandassente "
"samādapente samuttejente sampahaṃsente ahudeva akkhanti ahu appaccayo:"
msgstr "“Indeed, Kassapa, you made a mistake."

msgctxt "an3.91:4.2"
msgid "‘adhisallikhatevāyaṃ samaṇo’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:4.3"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho tvaṃ, kassapa, accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ paṭikarosi, "
"taṃ te mayaṃ paṭiggaṇhāma."
msgstr ""
"But since you have recognized your mistake for what it is, and have dealt "
"with it properly, I accept it."

msgctxt "an3.91:4.4"
msgid ""
"Vuddhihesā, kassapa, ariyassa vinaye yo accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ "
"paṭikaroti, āyatiṃ saṃvaraṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"For it is growth in the training of the noble one to recognize a mistake for "
"what it is, deal with it properly, and commit to restraint in the future."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:5.1"
msgid ""
"Thero cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti na sikkhākāmo na sikkhāsamādānassa "
"vaṇṇavādī, ye caññe bhikkhū na sikkhākāmā te ca na sikkhāya samādapeti, ye "
"caññe bhikkhū sikkhākāmā tesañca na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, "
"evarūpassāhaṃ, kassapa, therassa bhikkhuno na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr ""
"Kassapa, take the case of a senior mendicant who doesn’t want to train and "
"doesn’t praise taking up the training. They don’t encourage other mendicants "
"who don’t want to train to take up the training. And they don’t truthfully "
"and substantively praise at the right time those mendicants who do want to "
"train. I don’t praise that kind of senior mendicant."

msgctxt "an3.91:5.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an3.91:5.3"
msgid ""
"Satthā hissa vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇatīti aññe naṃ bhikkhū bhajeyyuṃ, ye naṃ bhajeyyuṃ "
"tyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ, yyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ "
"assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāyāti."
msgstr ""
"Because, hearing that I praised that mendicant, other mendicants might want "
"to keep company with them. Then they might follow their example, which would "
"be for their lasting harm and suffering."

msgctxt "an3.91:5.4"
msgid "Tasmāhaṃ, kassapa, evarūpassa therassa bhikkhuno na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr "That’s why I don’t praise that kind of senior mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.239"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:6.1"
msgid "Majjhimo cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti … pe …"
msgstr "Take the case of a middle mendicant who doesn’t want to train …"

msgctxt "an3.91:6.2"
msgid ""
"navo cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti na sikkhākāmo na sikkhāsamādānassa "
"vaṇṇavādī, ye caññe bhikkhū na sikkhākāmā te ca na sikkhāya samādapeti, ye "
"caññe bhikkhū sikkhākāmā tesañca na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, "
"evarūpassāhaṃ, kassapa, navassa bhikkhuno na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr "Take the case of a junior mendicant who doesn’t want to train …"

msgctxt "an3.91:6.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:6.4"
msgid ""
"Satthā hissa vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇatīti aññe naṃ bhikkhū bhajeyyuṃ, ye naṃ bhajeyyuṃ "
"tyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ, yyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ "
"assa dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāyāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:6.5"
msgid "Tasmāhaṃ, kassapa, evarūpassa navassa bhikkhuno na vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr "That’s why I don’t praise that kind of junior mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:7.1"
msgid ""
"Thero cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti sikkhākāmo sikkhāsamādānassa vaṇṇavādī, ye "
"caññe bhikkhū na sikkhākāmā te ca sikkhāya samādapeti, ye caññe bhikkhū "
"sikkhākāmā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, evarūpassāhaṃ, "
"kassapa, therassa bhikkhuno vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr ""
"Kassapa, take the case of a senior mendicant who does want to train and "
"praises taking up the training. They encourage other mendicants who don’t "
"want to train to take up the training. And they truthfully and substantively "
"praise at the right time those mendicants who do want to train. I praise "
"that kind of senior mendicant."

msgctxt "an3.91:7.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an3.91:7.3"
msgid ""
"Satthā hissa vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇatīti aññe naṃ bhikkhū bhajeyyuṃ, ye naṃ bhajeyyuṃ "
"tyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ, yyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ "
"assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyāti."
msgstr ""
"Because, hearing that I praised that mendicant, other mendicants might want "
"to keep company with them. Then they might follow their example, which would "
"be for their lasting welfare and happiness."

msgctxt "an3.91:7.4"
msgid "Tasmāhaṃ, kassapa, evarūpassa therassa bhikkhuno vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr "That’s why I praise that kind of senior mendicant."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:8.1"
msgid "Majjhimo cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti sikkhākāmo … pe …"
msgstr "Take the case of a middle mendicant who wants to train …"

msgctxt "an3.91:8.2"
msgid ""
"navo cepi, kassapa, bhikkhu hoti sikkhākāmo sikkhāsamādānassa vaṇṇavādī, ye "
"caññe bhikkhū na sikkhākāmā te ca sikkhāya samādapeti, ye caññe bhikkhū "
"sikkhākāmā tesañca vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇati bhūtaṃ tacchaṃ kālena, evarūpassāhaṃ, "
"kassapa, navassa bhikkhuno vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmi."
msgstr "Take the case of a junior mendicant who wants to train …"

msgctxt "an3.91:8.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:8.4"
msgid ""
"Satthā hissa vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇatīti aññe naṃ bhikkhū bhajeyyuṃ, ye naṃ bhajeyyuṃ "
"tyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ, yyāssa diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjeyyuṃ tesaṃ taṃ "
"assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an3.91:8.5"
msgid "Tasmāhaṃ, kassapa, evarūpassa navassa bhikkhuno vaṇṇaṃ bhaṇāmī”ti."
msgstr "That’s why I praise that kind of junior mendicant.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.91:8.6"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.91:8.7"
msgid "Samaṇavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an3.91:9.1"
msgid "Samaṇo gadrabho khettaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.91:9.2"
msgid "vajjiputto ca sekkhakaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.91:9.3"
msgid "Tayo ca sikkhanā vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.91:9.4"
msgid "dve sikkhā saṅkavāya cāti."
msgstr ""
